{"tid":2258353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友之間嘅信任破裂咗係咪冇辦法修補？","createTime":"2020-10-26T03:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T13:02:07.000Z","uid":134103,"like":6,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"374308058688b183e957711398e5c481eb7362e7","tid":2258353,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"我份人性格比較頑皮，成日講大話撚鳩個朋友，例如隻手整親瘀咗一大撻，我會同佢講係跳Joker dance唔小心碌落樓梯跌傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n初時覺得成功撚到佢好好笑，但係久而久之我講咩佢都唔信，我先察覺出事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似有一日我喺街跌咗銀包，身上一毫子都冇，要行路返屋企，諗住佢會借廿蚊俾我搭車返屋企，點知講咗好耐佢都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得朋友之間嘅信任一旦破裂咗，係咪真係冇辦法修補？<br />\n<br />\n又有冇巴絲可以講下類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以搶救下，睇你嘅誠意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上IFC排隊跳樓啦你"},{"pid":"7487fb272c71d09cfa7d58333bfe44138b664514","tid":2258353,"uid":27210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"關係由破壞中建立"},{"pid":"a8f0c50c3ac38b77e47c46cc3676c20c1c81867d","tid":2258353,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7487fb272c71d09cfa7d58333bfe44138b664514","tid":2258353,"uid":27210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"關係由破壞中建立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"好玄喎Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ab0aabc21a7b429fa7b0941dd4d19c13efd535","tid":2258353,"uid":34413,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T03:47:49.000Z","msg":"唔信你都正常 點知你邊句真邊句假"},{"pid":"cfcb7594b39191a4891c